predictions.article: Trade war escalation: Midwest farmers face uncertain future
predictions.prediction: The imposition of new tariffs by the U.S. on Mexico, Canada, and China will lead to a decrease in U.S. agricultural exports to these countries by at least 10% within the next two months.

predictions.article: Trade war escalates as retaliatory tariffs hit struggling farm economy
predictions.prediction: Retaliatory tariffs from China, Canada, and Mexico will cause U.S. soybean and corn prices to drop by at least 5% within the next month.
